---
// 도입 문의 — 라이트 강조 패널(cta-banner). /DESIGN.md 참조.
---
<section id="contact" class="border-b border-hairline">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-24">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-hairline bg-surface-1 px-6 py-14 text-center md:px-12 md:py-16">
      <p class="mb-4 text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.14em] text-primary">도입 문의</p>
      <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em] text-ink md:text-4xl">
        MediCount 도입을 검토 중이신가요?
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-md text-base leading-relaxed text-ink-subtle">
        병원·공급사 도입 문의를 받고 있습니다. 편하게 연락 주세요.
      </p>
      <a
        href="mailto:support@medicountapp.com"
        data-ga-event="cta_contact"
        data-ga-location="contact_section"
        class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-lg bg-primary px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-primary-hover"
      >
        support@medicountapp.com
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
